        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, crumble your <strong>feta</strong> into small bite-sized pieces</p><p>Add the <strong>crumbled feta </strong>to a bowl with your <strong>natural yoghurt </strong>and a grind of <strong>black pepper </strong>and stir it all together – this is your <strong>feta yoghurt</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
