      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once thickened, make 1 well per person in the pan, then crack your <strong>egg[s] </strong>into the well[s] and cook, covered, for 2-3 min or until the egg is done to your liking – this is your <strong>cannellini bean shakshuka</strong></p><p>Tip: Give your egg a little shake before you crack for a perfectly centred yolk!</p>",
