    {
      "instruction": "<p>Slice your<strong> ciabatta[s]</strong> in half and place in the <strong>toaster</strong> for 1-2 min or until toasted</p><p>Once toasted, slice the <strong>toasted ciabatta halves </strong>on the diagonal</p>",
