    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>cannellini bean shakshuka</strong> with the <strong>feta yoghurt</strong> and <strong>toasted ciabatta[s] </strong>to the side</p><p>Garnish with your <strong>pumpkin seeds</strong>, a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and a grind of <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
